  "description": "A vibrant and dramatic image of a sunset featuring a layered cloudscape. The sky transitions from deep oranges and reds near the horizon to darker shades as it ascends. The clouds are horizontally stretched, creating a sense of movement and depth.  The composition is largely defined by the striking contrast between the bright, warm tones of the clouds and the darker upper portions of the image.  There is a very dark, almost silhouetted suggestion of land or mountains at the very top of the frame. The light is diffused and creates a soft glow around the cloud edges.",
